{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751010/extras/Desc1.png?t=1723787893\" /><br><strong>Galaxy Too Far</strong> gives you control over AI system. The main goal is to be useful for your Creator and you finally found a good planet to make it a resource base.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751010/extras/Desc2.png?t=1723787893\" /><br>Start your expansion with the most basic structures. Use the mining system to extract resources. Perform primary processing, and then create your first technological materials. While drones help you to transfer fragile materials, pipelines move heavy raw resources.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751010/extras/Desc3.png?t=1723787893\" /><br>Start investigating energy resources available on the alien planet. From classic wind and solar energy to geothermal and cosmic radiation.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751010/extras/Desc6.png?t=1723787893\" /><br>Terrain based gameplay. Ground level, biome type, water level matter.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751010/extras/Desc7.png?t=1723787893\" /><br>Complex Augmentation system. Helps you to determine where you can build a specific building, how it will be connected to other systems. Where underground resource is located, what temperature is in the hovering building spot and more.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751010/extras/Desc4.png?t=1723787893\" /><br>Close the ring around the planet and prepare the Beacon for a final strike. It will require a lot of resources and energy to accomplish. Use orbital constructions to support your planet infrastructure.<br><br><img